00:04:45.720 --> 00:04:48.680
One day, I stumbled into a cave

00:04:48.950 --> 00:04:51.040
and met the spiritual body
of an immortal.

00:04:51.540 --> 00:04:54.160
She was shrouded
in a soul-devouring aura.

00:04:54.920 --> 00:04:56.510
The moment I drew close,

00:04:56.510 --> 00:04:58.560
